    <abstract>
      <t>TI-LFA specifies fast protections for transit nodes and links of an SR path. However, it does not present any fast protections for the egress node of the SR path. This document describes protocol extensions for fast protecting the egress node and link of a Segment Routing for IPv6 (SRv6) path.</t>
